From the above results and discussion, we can conclude that the one-pot method described here is the easiest method to make the precursor solution necessary to have the nano octahedron shape architecture along with cauliflower type morphology. The detailed morphological investigation of the film reveals that the particular concentration and solvothermal reaction time helps in obtaining the desired morphology. Concerning the chemistry in this work, we would like to point out that, our main goal is to show the photoelectrochemical response of the cauliflower and octahedron shaped hematite architec-
